{"tid":596681,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚4月中去福岡既巴絲交流下","createTime":"2018-03-18T01:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T12:50:45.000Z","uid":75021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ed769dabaa71468e561ed9d389a663645f2040","tid":596681,"uid":75021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T01:41:34.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲分享下自己既行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時淨係睇左少少 未得閒plan 住<br />\n應該都係去熊本 阿蘇 福岡市買下野<br />\n去七日 求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己偏好行公園 神社 睇風景多"},{"pid":"c253e3a43b6c02e4e80ffad23fbe286df8291bd7","tid":596681,"uid":25149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"4月都係去福岡，諗緊布院究竟點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580ddc8cc35b9d08473ca6ebc417c2c38c36be40","tid":596681,"uid":155012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:18:47.000Z","msg":"諗住5月去，咩都未plan"},{"pid":"29f30efddaea7dfc6b179db879d3ab609b86a046","tid":596681,"uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:24:48.000Z","msg":"4月去自駕 會落長崎同由布院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1acaa2a687a624d3f04d1fc6ecfea01ba342bb","tid":596681,"uid":21780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T16:58:11.000Z","msg":"7月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下咁多位諗住去由布院既巴打係幾多人去同諗住book邊間？<br />\n本身睇中左由布之彩，但我5個人去，好似突左個個都要比2個人錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以睇緊由布乃庄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb43730dc2f8d01394b21fc71fafa5701531561","tid":596681,"uid":75021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T16:00:19.000Z","msg